## Environment Variables

| Variable | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `LOG_LEVEL` | `info` | Logging verbosity. One of `debug`, `info`, `warn`, `error`. |
| `RATE_LIMIT_MAX` | `100` | Max requests per minute per client (HTTP variants only). |
